[SPEAKER_00] da vam se zbrišu gresi

672
00:42:52,719 --> 00:42:54,840
[SPEAKER_00] tako da od gospodnje prisutnosti

673
00:42:54,840 --> 00:42:56,699
[SPEAKER_00] mogu doći vremena utjehe

674
00:42:56,699 --> 00:42:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] Duda Fučak prevode

675
00:42:58,360 --> 00:42:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] vremena rashlade

676
00:42:59,539 --> 00:43:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] i da on pošalje

677
00:43:01,280 --> 00:43:02,360
[SPEAKER_00] pred određenog vam

678
00:43:02,360 --> 00:43:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] Mesiju Isusa

679
00:43:03,340 --> 00:43:05,440
[SPEAKER_00] onog kojeg nebo

680
00:43:05,440 --> 00:43:06,800
[SPEAKER_00] treba da pridrži

681
00:43:06,800 --> 00:43:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] do vremena sveopće obnove

682
00:43:08,539 --> 00:43:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] koje je Bog navijestio

683
00:43:10,199 --> 00:43:11,320
[SPEAKER_00] preko svojih proroka.

684
00:43:11,320 --> 00:43:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se događa?

685
00:43:12,579 --> 00:43:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Petar kaže

686
00:43:13,380 --> 00:43:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] da će nebo

687
00:43:14,659 --> 00:43:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] pridržat Mesiju

688
00:43:15,980 --> 00:43:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] do njegovog drugog dolaska

689
00:43:17,420 --> 00:43:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] i da prvo treba doći utjehaj rasklada

690
00:43:20,159 --> 00:43:22,219
[SPEAKER_00] koja treba ljude dovesti do obnove.

691
00:43:22,219 --> 00:43:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] I to se događa danas

692
00:43:24,900 --> 00:43:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] kroz karizmatski pokret.

693
00:43:26,039 --> 00:43:27,659
[SPEAKER_00] Samo znate ko je problem glavni?

694
00:43:27,659 --> 00:43:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] Što smo mi ostali na toj raskladi.

695
00:43:32,139 --> 00:43:34,679
[SPEAKER_00] Karizmatski pokret je osnato da dolazimo i lijepo nam je.

696
00:43:34,679 --> 00:43:35,639
[SPEAKER_00] Mi se punimo,

697
00:43:35,639 --> 00:43:37,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali ništa ne dajemo.

698
00:43:37,320 --> 00:43:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nam daje tu snagu i tu silu duha svetog

699
00:43:40,800 --> 00:43:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] da preobražavamo svijet oko sebe.

700
00:43:44,780 --> 00:43:48,719
[SPEAKER_00] i odgovarat će oni koji su primili tu puninu i tu silu,

701
00:43:48,719 --> 00:43:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] a ostali su se hladiti.

702
00:43:51,780 --> 00:43:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] A to se događa.

703
00:43:52,659 --> 00:43:54,079
[SPEAKER_00] Probudite se.

704
00:43:54,079 --> 00:43:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste isto dio toga.

705
00:43:55,300 --> 00:43:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je dao tu silu,

706
00:43:58,760 --> 00:43:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] to pomazanje,

707
00:43:59,559 --> 00:44:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] doslovce izlio novu vodu,

708
00:44:01,400 --> 00:44:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] živu vodu na vas

709
00:44:02,519 --> 00:44:04,659
[SPEAKER_00] da nastane vrijeme obnove,

710
00:44:04,659 --> 00:44:07,179
[SPEAKER_00] jer Bog podiže svoja dva naroda.

711
00:44:07,179 --> 00:44:10,300
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo, to se događa početak 20. stoljeća.

712
00:44:10,300 --> 00:44:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] Otprilike u isto vrijeme,

713
00:44:11,579 --> 00:44:14,820
[SPEAKER_00] 1897. javlja se inicijativa

714
00:44:14,820 --> 00:44:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] i to od austro-ugarskog novinara,

715
00:44:16,980 --> 00:44:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] židovskog porijekla,

716
00:44:17,960 --> 00:44:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] Terodor Herzla,

717
00:44:19,099 --> 00:44:21,760
[SPEAKER_00] da se Izraelci skupe iz cijelog

718
00:44:21,760 --> 00:44:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] svijeta i vrate u obećanu zemlju.

719
00:44:24,480 --> 00:44:26,800
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo, u isto vrijeme,

720
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:29,300
[SPEAKER_00] Bog podiže i smokvu i lozu.

721
00:44:29,300 --> 00:44:30,599
[SPEAKER_00] To je 20. stoljeć.

722
00:44:30,599 --> 00:44:32,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je bit te obnove?

723
00:44:32,780 --> 00:44:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva se mora vratit

724
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:37,280
[SPEAKER_00] u svoju duhovnu baštinu

725
00:44:37,280 --> 00:44:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] koja je pripada,

726
00:44:38,019 --> 00:44:39,440
[SPEAKER_00] a to je da dijeluje u sili,

727
00:44:39,440 --> 00:44:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] da bude izraz Božje snage,

728
00:44:41,840 --> 00:44:43,159
[SPEAKER_00] da se događaju čudesa,

729
00:44:43,159 --> 00:44:45,280
[SPEAKER_00] da utječe na ljude oko sebe,

730
00:44:45,280 --> 00:44:47,860
[SPEAKER_00] a Izrael se treba vratit

731
00:44:47,860 --> 00:44:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] u svoju fizičku domovinu.

732
00:44:49,340 --> 00:44:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo ta dva povratka

733
00:44:51,739 --> 00:44:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] u 20. stoljeću.

734
00:44:53,119 --> 00:44:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] I normalno,

735
00:44:53,880 --> 00:44:57,440
[SPEAKER_00] kogod je imalo u duhovnosti,

736
00:44:57,440 --> 00:44:59,219
[SPEAKER_00] može razumjeti zašto je nastao

737
00:44:59,219 --> 00:45:00,820
[SPEAKER_00] drugi svjetski rat i komunizam.

738
00:45:00,820 --> 00:45:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] Cijel je bio u Holokaustu

739
00:45:04,099 --> 00:45:05,659
[SPEAKER_00] ugušiti tu obnovu

740
00:45:05,659 --> 00:45:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] izraelskog naroda

741
00:45:06,519 --> 00:45:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] i njegov povratak

742
00:45:07,619 --> 00:45:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] u obećanu zemlju,

743
00:45:09,039 --> 00:45:10,420
[SPEAKER_00] a kroz komunizam

744
00:45:10,420 --> 00:45:11,780
[SPEAKER_00] uništit crkvu.

745
00:45:13,519 --> 00:45:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] Nije uspjelo.

746
00:45:14,159 --> 00:45:17,019
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je vjeran svoje riječi

747
00:45:17,019 --> 00:45:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] i Božja riječ će se uvijek ispuniti.

748
00:45:18,840 --> 00:45:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] I sad vidimo

749
00:45:20,900 --> 00:45:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] da je čak i taj Holokaust

750
00:45:22,599 --> 00:45:23,940
[SPEAKER_00] bio najavljen

751
00:45:23,940 --> 00:45:26,219
[SPEAKER_00] već kod proroka Jeremije.

752
00:45:26,219 --> 00:45:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite šta Jeremija govori

753
00:45:28,619 --> 00:45:32,340
[SPEAKER_00] svome narodu.

754
00:45:32,340 --> 00:45:45,739
[SPEAKER_00] U vrijeme izgnanstva im kaže ovako.

755
00:45:45,739 --> 00:45:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] Evo riječi što Jahve reče

756
00:45:48,579 --> 00:45:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] o Izraelu i Judeji.

757
00:45:49,619 --> 00:45:51,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako govori Jahve,

758
00:45:51,340 --> 00:45:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] čujem krik užasa,

759
00:45:52,619 --> 00:45:53,679
[SPEAKER_00] strava je to,

760
00:45:53,679 --> 00:45:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] a ne mir.

761
00:45:54,480 --> 00:45:56,039
[SPEAKER_00] Tu govori o povratku

762
00:45:56,039 --> 00:45:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] i vidi se da se ne radi o povratku

763
00:45:58,300 --> 00:45:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] iz Babilonskog sužanstva

764
00:45:59,639 --> 00:46:02,320
[SPEAKER_00] ili iz Babilona su se oni vraćali mirnim.

765
00:46:02,340 --> 00:46:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] putem.

766
00:46:02,800 --> 00:46:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] I dalje kaže jednu jako

767
00:46:04,519 --> 00:46:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] provokativnu rečenicu i pitanje.

768
00:46:06,420 --> 00:46:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, hajde propitajte se i pogledajte

769
00:46:08,920 --> 00:46:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] je li ikad muškarac rodio,

770
00:46:10,900 --> 00:46:13,320
[SPEAKER_00] a svi se muškarci za bedra

771
00:46:13,320 --> 00:46:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] hvataju kao porodilje.

772
00:46:14,800 --> 00:46:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto su sva lica izobličena

773
00:46:17,380 --> 00:46:18,519
[SPEAKER_00] i problijedjela?

774
00:46:18,519 --> 00:46:20,780
[SPEAKER_00] Jel su vam poznati ove slike?

775
00:46:20,780 --> 00:46:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] Poslušite još jednom Jeremiju.

776
00:46:24,920 --> 00:46:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] Hajde propitajte se i pogledajte

777
00:46:27,099 --> 00:46:28,559
[SPEAKER_00] je li ikad muškarac rodio,

778
00:46:28,559 --> 00:46:30,500
[SPEAKER_00] a svi se muškarci za bedra

779
00:46:30,500 --> 00:46:31,980
[SPEAKER_00] hvataju kao porodilje,

780
00:46:32,340 --> 00:46:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] zašto su sva lica izobličena

781
00:46:34,340 --> 00:46:35,260
[SPEAKER_00] i izbredjela.

782
00:46:35,260 --> 00:46:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jeremija na kraju tog proroštva

783
00:46:37,960 --> 00:46:39,260
[SPEAKER_00] im jasno daje do znanja

784
00:46:39,260 --> 00:46:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] da se to odnosi na posljednja vremena,

785
00:46:41,159 --> 00:46:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] a po katekizmu mi živimo

786
00:46:42,500 --> 00:46:43,639
[SPEAKER_00] u posljednjim vremenima.

787
00:46:43,639 --> 00:46:44,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

788
00:46:44,519 --> 00:46:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jahvin se gnjev neće stišati

789
00:46:46,920 --> 00:46:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] dok on ne izvrši

790
00:46:47,980 --> 00:46:49,840
[SPEAKER_00] i ne ispuni naume srca svojega.

791
00:46:49,840 --> 00:46:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže ovako,

792
00:46:51,000 --> 00:46:52,139
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju proroštva,

793
00:46:52,139 --> 00:46:53,820
[SPEAKER_00] u dane posljednje

794
00:46:53,820 --> 00:46:55,639
[SPEAKER_00] jasno ćete to razumijet.

795
00:46:56,400 --> 00:46:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo proroštvo za posljednje dane

796
00:46:58,440 --> 00:47:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] gdje opisuje povratak Izraela

797
00:47:00,059 --> 00:47:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] kroz tu zadnju veliku patnju

798
00:47:02,820 --> 00:47:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] koja će prethoditi njihovom povratku

799
00:47:05,840 --> 00:47:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] u običanu zemlju.

800
00:47:13,400 --> 00:47:15,320
[SPEAKER_00] I sad dolazi njihov povratak

801
00:47:15,320 --> 00:47:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] u običanu zemlju

802
00:47:16,119 --> 00:47:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] koji se dogodio

803
00:47:16,940 --> 00:47:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] 1947. i 1948. godine.

804
00:47:21,239 --> 00:47:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo,

805
00:47:22,159 --> 00:47:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] polako je rastao broj židova,

806
00:47:24,420 --> 00:47:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] taj sionistički pokret

807
00:47:25,699 --> 00:47:27,239
[SPEAKER_00] koji je krenuo zajedno

808
00:47:27,239 --> 00:47:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] sa karizmatskim pokretom

809
00:47:29,340 --> 00:47:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] je naseljavao

810
00:47:31,119 --> 00:47:32,519
[SPEAKER_00] sve više i više Izraelaca.

811
00:47:32,519 --> 00:47:34,719
[SPEAKER_00] I vidimo malo,

812
00:47:34,719 --> 00:47:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] taj povratak

813
00:47:36,880 --> 00:47:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] najavi već 750. prije Krista

814
00:47:39,960 --> 00:47:41,179
[SPEAKER_00] po proroku Ezekijelu,

815
00:47:41,179 --> 00:47:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] a ispunio se

816
00:47:41,900 --> 00:47:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] 1948.

817
00:47:43,519 --> 00:47:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo,

818
00:47:48,039 --> 00:47:48,679
[SPEAKER_00] u onaj dan,

819
00:47:48,679 --> 00:47:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] vidimo šta je Izaja rekao,

820
00:47:50,599 --> 00:47:52,360
[SPEAKER_00] Jahve će drugi put ruku pružiti

821
00:47:52,360 --> 00:47:54,159
[SPEAKER_00] da je otkupio statak svoga naroda,

822
00:47:54,159 --> 00:47:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] podignuće stijeg narodima,

823
00:47:56,260 --> 00:47:58,179
[SPEAKER_00] sabraće Izraelu prognanike

824
00:47:58,179 --> 00:47:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] i skupiti ude

825
00:47:59,039 --> 00:48:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] raspršene sa sva četiri kraja zemlje.

826
00:48:01,500 --> 00:48:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo,

827
00:48:05,260 --> 00:48:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] to je povratak Izraelaca.

828
00:48:07,059 --> 00:48:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je sociološko

829
00:48:09,440 --> 00:48:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] i antropološko čudo.

830
00:48:11,280 --> 00:48:13,179
[SPEAKER_00] probajte si zamisliti da jedan narod

831
00:48:13,179 --> 00:48:14,940
[SPEAKER_00] dvije tisuće godina

832
00:48:14,940 --> 00:48:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] je raseljen okolo po drugim narodima

833
00:48:17,639 --> 00:48:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] i preko sto zemalja.

834
00:48:19,619 --> 00:48:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] U Izrael su se doselili ljudi

835
00:48:21,679 --> 00:48:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] iz sto zemalja.

836
00:48:22,940 --> 00:48:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] I da sačuvaju svoj jezik,

837
00:48:25,059 --> 00:48:26,780
[SPEAKER_00] pripadnost,

838
00:48:26,780 --> 00:48:28,079
[SPEAKER_00] plemenu,

839
00:48:28,079 --> 00:48:29,280
[SPEAKER_00] kojem pripadaju,

840
00:48:29,280 --> 00:48:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] i svoju vjeru.

841
00:48:32,340 --> 00:48:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] Osobno poznajem treća generacija

842
00:48:34,340 --> 00:48:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] i u Argentini Hrvata i Australije više ne govori hrvatski jezik.

843
00:48:38,059 --> 00:48:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] Jedva ih se može razumjeti.

844
00:48:39,980 --> 00:48:41,099
[SPEAKER_00] Treća generacija.

845
00:48:41,099 --> 00:48:44,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dvije tisuće godina izraelski narod bio raširen

846
00:48:44,800 --> 00:48:46,760
[SPEAKER_00] među sto drugih naroda

847
00:48:46,760 --> 00:48:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji su ih mrzeli i htjeli istrijebiti

848
00:48:48,119 --> 00:48:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] i uspjeveo se vratiti.

849
00:48:50,619 --> 00:48:53,780
[SPEAKER_00] To nijedan sociolog, nijedan antropolog ne može objasniti.

850
00:48:53,780 --> 00:48:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je čudo i fenomen

851
00:48:55,460 --> 00:48:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] i još jedan dokaz tog nadnaravnog izraelskog poziva.

852
00:48:58,940 --> 00:49:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] Jezekiel, 36. poglavlje,

853
00:49:02,860 --> 00:49:05,440
[SPEAKER_00] kaže ovako, 24. redak,

854
00:49:05,440 --> 00:49:07,260
[SPEAKER_00] tada ću vas sabrati iz svih naroda

855
00:49:07,260 --> 00:49:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] i skupiti iz svih zemalja

856
00:49:08,579 --> 00:49:10,699
[SPEAKER_00] i natrag vas doveti u vašu zemlju.

857
00:49:10,699 --> 00:49:12,739
[SPEAKER_00] I nastanit ćete se u zemlji

858
00:49:12,739 --> 00:49:13,980
[SPEAKER_00] koju dadoh vašim ocima

859
00:49:13,980 --> 00:49:16,139
[SPEAKER_00] i bit ćete moj narod, a ja ću biti vaš bog.

860
00:49:16,139 --> 00:49:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] I točno opisuje kako će to biti.

861
00:49:18,260 --> 00:49:22,239
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo će ih sabrati ponovo u Izrael,

862
00:49:22,239 --> 00:49:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] a tek onda će nastupiti obračenje

863
00:49:24,699 --> 00:49:27,019
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem će oni njega prepoznat kao mesiju

864
00:49:27,019 --> 00:49:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] gdje će se pokajati.

865
00:49:28,300 --> 00:49:30,659
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, prvo ide njihov dolazak,

866
00:49:30,659 --> 00:49:32,239
[SPEAKER_00] a onda objava.

867
00:49:32,239 --> 00:49:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] Jezekiel nam daje još neke zanimljive činjenice

868
00:49:36,460 --> 00:49:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] kao, napući ću opet vaše gradove,

869
00:49:40,940 --> 00:49:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] sadek živi 8 milijuna tamo,

870
00:49:43,780 --> 00:49:45,659
[SPEAKER_00] i sagradit razvaline.

871
00:49:45,659 --> 00:49:47,900
[SPEAKER_00] Opustila zemlja, nekoć pustinja,

872
00:49:47,900 --> 00:49:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] na očigled svakom prolazniku,

873
00:49:50,199 --> 00:49:51,519
[SPEAKER_00] bit će opet obrađena.

874
00:49:51,519 --> 00:49:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] I tada će reći, evo zemlje što bijaš se pusta,

875
00:49:54,460 --> 00:49:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] a postane kao vrt edenski.

876
00:49:56,340 --> 00:49:58,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, neko od vas bio u Izraelu?

877
00:49:58,800 --> 00:50:00,239
[SPEAKER_00] Je li je?

878
00:50:00,239 --> 00:50:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je?

879
00:50:00,519 --> 00:50:03,179
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je pustinja,

880
00:50:03,179 --> 00:50:04,820
[SPEAKER_00] a sve je cvijeta.

881
00:50:04,820 --> 00:50:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] Cvijeć.

882
00:50:06,480 --> 00:50:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] Točno kako je Jezekiel rekao.

883
00:50:07,920 --> 00:50:10,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo su slike danas u Izraelskoj pustinji.

884
00:50:10,780 --> 00:50:14,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo se čak zove vrt edenski,

885
00:50:14,119 --> 00:50:15,659
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj nacionalni park tamo.

886
00:50:15,659 --> 00:50:17,219
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je navodnjavano,

887
00:50:17,219 --> 00:50:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] sve je cvate.

888
00:50:18,239 --> 00:50:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je Jezekiel rekao,

889
00:50:20,539 --> 00:50:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] a to je taj znak će pratiti

890
00:50:22,340 --> 00:50:24,539
[SPEAKER_00] povratak Izraela u običanu zemlju.

891
00:50:28,539 --> 00:50:32,840
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, da ne vidim ili dobro pratite,

892
00:50:32,840 --> 00:50:36,360
[SPEAKER_00] koje je stabla Izraela?

893
00:50:36,360 --> 00:50:38,760
[SPEAKER_00] Smokva ili smokva?

894
00:50:38,760 --> 00:50:41,559
[SPEAKER_00] I Isus nam daje,

895
00:50:41,559 --> 00:50:44,699
[SPEAKER_00] Isus se koristi tom usporedbom.

896
00:50:44,699 --> 00:50:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] I pazite sad ovo,

897
00:50:46,599 --> 00:50:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] u Lukinom evanđelju,

898
00:50:47,920 --> 00:50:49,760
[SPEAKER_00] a ovo je za vas.

899
00:50:49,760 --> 00:50:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] To je za vas,

900
00:50:51,179 --> 00:50:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] jer ovo je proroštvo za posljednja vremena.

901
00:50:53,440 --> 00:50:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže ovako,

902
00:50:56,960 --> 00:50:58,739
[SPEAKER_00] Pojavit će se znaci na suncu,

903
00:50:58,739 --> 00:50:59,940
[SPEAKER_00] imamo Fatimu,

904
00:50:59,940 --> 00:51:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] ne želim nam ništa insinuirati,

905
00:51:01,500 --> 00:51:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] vi sami procijenite,

906
00:51:02,619 --> 00:51:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] jel se nalazim u tom vremenu.

907
00:51:04,000 --> 00:51:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] Pojavit će se znaci na suncu,

908
00:51:05,980 --> 00:51:07,119
[SPEAKER_00] mjesecu i zvijezdama.

909
00:51:07,119 --> 00:51:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] Na zemlji će narodi biti u tijeskobi

910
00:51:10,199 --> 00:51:12,719
[SPEAKER_00] i neizvjesnosti zbog huke morskih valova.

911
00:51:12,719 --> 00:51:15,099
[SPEAKER_00] Šta smo imali sad sa uraganom mirma.

912
00:51:15,099 --> 00:51:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi će umirati od straha

913
00:51:17,340 --> 00:51:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] u očekivanja onog što će zadesiti svijet,

914
00:51:19,420 --> 00:51:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] jer zvježdja nebeska će se uzdrmati.

915
00:51:21,400 --> 00:51:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tada ćete vidjeti sina čoveče

916
00:51:23,559 --> 00:51:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] gdje dolazi na oblaku s velikom moći i slavom.

917
00:51:26,039 --> 00:51:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] To je proces koji će trajati.

918
00:51:28,699 --> 00:51:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] Zato Isus kaže,

919
00:51:29,460 --> 00:51:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] kad to počne bivati,

920
00:51:31,119 --> 00:51:33,559
[SPEAKER_00] znači vidimo da se počeci već tu,

921
00:51:33,559 --> 00:51:35,260
[SPEAKER_00] kad to počne bivati,

922
00:51:35,260 --> 00:51:37,280
[SPEAKER_00] uspravite se i podignite glave,

923
00:51:37,280 --> 00:51:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] jer je blizu vaše oslobođenje.

924
00:51:39,420 --> 00:51:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] I zatim im reče usporedbu.

925
00:51:42,400 --> 00:51:44,039
[SPEAKER_00] A sad ovo je prenezeno značenje,

926
00:51:44,039 --> 00:51:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali kaže usporedbu.

927
00:51:45,099 --> 00:51:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte smokvu,

928
00:51:47,579 --> 00:51:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] a to je Izrael,

929
00:51:49,619 --> 00:51:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] i sva ostala stabla.

930
00:51:52,099 --> 00:51:54,760
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ih vidite da već pupe,

931
00:51:54,760 --> 00:51:57,440
[SPEAKER_00] znate sami od sebe da je blizu ljeto.

932
00:51:57,440 --> 00:52:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tako i vi kad vidite da to biva,

933
00:52:00,119 --> 00:52:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] znajte da je blizu kraljevstvo Božje.

934
00:52:03,380 --> 00:52:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] Znači dajem usporedbu,

935
00:52:04,559 --> 00:52:06,739
[SPEAKER_00] kad vidite smokvu i ostala stabla,

936
00:52:06,739 --> 00:52:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] znajte da je blizu kraljevstvo,

937
00:52:09,760 --> 00:52:11,019
[SPEAKER_00] da već pupe,

938
00:52:11,019 --> 00:52:13,300
[SPEAKER_00] značite da je blizu kraljevstvo Božje.

939
00:52:13,300 --> 00:52:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je karta svijeta

940
00:52:16,840 --> 00:52:18,280
[SPEAKER_00] prije drugog svjetskog rata.

941
00:52:18,280 --> 00:52:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo, ovo je prije drugog svjetskog rata.

942
00:52:22,000 --> 00:52:25,739
[SPEAKER_00] Izrael je prva zemlja

943
00:52:25,739 --> 00:52:28,119
[SPEAKER_00] koja je pokrenula UN-u postupak

944
00:52:28,119 --> 00:52:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] za proglašenje neovisnosti

945
00:52:29,559 --> 00:52:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] od kolonijalnih vlasti.

946
00:52:32,260 --> 00:52:35,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog Izrela je preko što zemalja

947
00:52:35,820 --> 00:52:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] kasnije moglo dobiti neovisnost.

948
00:52:37,840 --> 00:52:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte nakon što je

949
00:52:40,559 --> 00:52:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] u petom mjesecu 48. priznati Izrael

950
00:52:43,340 --> 00:52:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] kako je zla karta svijeta.

951
00:52:44,920 --> 00:52:46,340
[SPEAKER_00] Sto novih zemalja.

952
00:52:46,340 --> 00:52:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] A Isus kaže,

953
00:52:47,460 --> 00:52:50,480
[SPEAKER_00] pogledajte smokvu i ostala stabla.

954
00:52:50,480 --> 00:52:51,659
[SPEAKER_00] To su drugi narodi.

955
00:52:51,659 --> 00:52:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kad vidite da već pupe,

956
00:52:53,019 --> 00:52:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] znajte da je blizu.

957
00:52:54,460 --> 00:53:01,139
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazimo na 14. proroštvo

958
00:53:01,139 --> 00:53:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] proroštvo u kojem sad živimo.

959
00:53:04,019 --> 00:53:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] Mi momentalno živimo u vrijeme

960
00:53:05,739 --> 00:53:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] ovog proroštva.

961
00:53:06,579 --> 00:53:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] Pola se je ispunilo,

962
00:53:07,659 --> 00:53:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] još pola se mora ispuniti.

963
00:53:09,159 --> 00:53:12,219
[SPEAKER_00] Rat mnogih naroda protiv Izrela.

964
00:53:12,219 --> 00:53:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] Prorećeno 750. prije Krista

965
00:53:15,119 --> 00:53:16,280
[SPEAKER_00] po proroku Zahari

966
00:53:16,280 --> 00:53:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] ispunja se u našim danima.

967
00:53:17,920 --> 00:53:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je 15. petog 1948.

968
00:53:21,579 --> 00:53:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] Izrael proglasio neovisnost,

969
00:53:23,599 --> 00:53:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] tri države su mu objavile rat isti dan.

970
00:53:27,800 --> 00:53:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte,

971
00:53:28,239 --> 00:53:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] otkad je Izrael tamo,

972
00:53:30,420 --> 00:53:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] nije bilo ni dana mira.

973
00:53:32,579 --> 00:53:33,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da se moglo već,

974
00:53:33,440 --> 00:53:35,639
[SPEAKER_00] tu je Izrael sad živi u potpuno miru,

975
00:53:35,639 --> 00:53:36,639
[SPEAKER_00] nema opasnosti.

976
00:53:36,639 --> 00:53:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tu razumite onaj džavolj i bijez

977
00:53:40,019 --> 00:53:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji postoji prema Izrelu.

978
00:53:41,340 --> 00:53:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] Druga polovica 20. stoljeća i dalje.

979
00:53:46,460 --> 00:53:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] Kažu,

980
00:53:46,820 --> 00:53:48,639
[SPEAKER_00] u onaj danu činit ću je Ruzlanim

981
00:53:48,639 --> 00:53:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] teškim kamenom svim narodima.

982
00:53:50,440 --> 00:53:51,739
[SPEAKER_00] Svi koji ga budu dizali,

983
00:53:51,739 --> 00:53:53,059
[SPEAKER_00] teško će se izraniti,

984
00:53:53,059 --> 00:53:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] a skupit će se na njih svi narodi zemlje.

985
00:53:55,699 --> 00:53:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] To se događa u naše vrijeme.

986
00:53:57,420 --> 00:53:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, htio bih vam samo,

987
00:53:58,460 --> 00:53:59,679
[SPEAKER_00] e sad da vidim,

988
00:53:59,679 --> 00:54:03,420
[SPEAKER_00] ima neko koji je 67. godine bio živ.

989
00:54:03,420 --> 00:54:06,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ima nas puno, dignite.

990
00:54:06,440 --> 00:54:10,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo 67. godište i dolje.

991
00:54:10,860 --> 00:54:13,059
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ovo je u naše vrijeme.

992
00:54:13,059 --> 00:54:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte kako je izgledao šestodnevni rat.

993
00:54:17,460 --> 00:54:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, kad čitam one neke

994
00:54:19,619 --> 00:54:22,400
[SPEAKER_00] biblijske priče,

995
00:54:22,400 --> 00:54:24,300
[SPEAKER_00] mnogi misle da je to pretirivanje.

996
00:54:24,300 --> 00:54:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad recimo Gideon dođe sa 30.000 vojnika

997
00:54:27,000 --> 00:54:29,840
[SPEAKER_00] ili koliko je onda mu Bog smanji na 300 vojnika

998
00:54:29,840 --> 00:54:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže, e s njima ćeš pobjediti.

999
00:54:31,420 --> 00:54:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ili dođe njih par na cijelo mnošto

1000
00:54:34,440 --> 00:54:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] i pobjedi ih.

1001
00:54:35,199 --> 00:54:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] Neki kažu da je to preneseno značenje isto.

1002
00:54:38,199 --> 00:54:40,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne vjerujem da je preneseno značenje.

1003
00:54:40,400 --> 00:54:43,559
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo dokaz da se to događalo u naše vrijeme.

1004
00:54:43,960 --> 00:54:47,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte ko se našao u šestodnevnom ratu

1005
00:54:47,559 --> 00:54:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] na jednoj strani, a pogledajmo ko je činio drugu koaliciju.

1006
00:54:50,900 --> 00:54:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] 5.6.67. u 8.45 minuta počeo rat.

1007
00:54:56,679 --> 00:55:03,179
[SPEAKER_00] 10.6.67. nakon 5.5 dana u 18.30 je rat savršio.

1008
00:55:03,179 --> 00:55:05,440
[SPEAKER_00] Službeno ovaj predaj na Sineu.

1009
00:55:05,440 --> 00:55:08,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam čak izračunao, išli sam računati

1010
00:55:08,519 --> 00:55:11,320
[SPEAKER_00] točno koliko naroda je bilo protiv koliko naroda.

1011
00:55:11,320 --> 00:55:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] Izrael je tad imao 6.5 milijuna židova,

1012
00:55:14,360 --> 00:55:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] a arapska koalicija 110 milijuna.

1013
00:55:18,599 --> 00:55:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] 6.5 milijuna, okruženi sa svih strana,

1014
00:55:22,460 --> 00:55:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] ovi su ih napali, ovi su ih ko jednog satrali, doslovci.

1015
00:55:27,539 --> 00:55:30,099
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je od se Božje obećanje, plan mora ispuniti.

1016
00:55:30,099 --> 00:55:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] Jordanski kralj Husein i Gamal Abdel Nasser,

1017
00:55:34,340 --> 00:55:37,760
[SPEAKER_00] koji je bio prijatelj Tita, nesretnog,

1018
00:55:37,760 --> 00:55:42,239
[SPEAKER_00] oni su skovali plan da unište Izrael.

1019
00:55:42,239 --> 00:55:47,219
[SPEAKER_00] I dok sam sprema ovu temu i dok sam čitao taj tekst,

1020
00:55:47,219 --> 00:55:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] tako mi je jasno u duhu došao drugi psalam,

1021
00:55:49,699 --> 00:55:55,719
[SPEAKER_00] koji je kao proroštvo doslovce za ovaj šestodneni rat.

1022
00:55:55,800 --> 00:55:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, zašto se bune narodi, zašto puci ludosti stuju?

1023
00:55:59,019 --> 00:56:00,679
[SPEAKER_00] Usta je u kraljevi zemaljski,

1024
00:56:00,679 --> 00:56:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] knezovi se rote protiv jahve i pomazanika njegova.

1025
00:56:03,880 --> 00:56:06,699
[SPEAKER_00] Skršimo okove njihove i jaram njihov zbacimo.

1026
00:56:06,699 --> 00:56:08,760
[SPEAKER_00] A, paljste Božji odgiver, kaže,

1027
00:56:08,760 --> 00:56:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] smije se one što na nebu stoluje,

1028
00:56:10,679 --> 00:56:12,059
[SPEAKER_00] gospod im se podruguje.

1029
00:56:12,059 --> 00:56:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] Urotili su se da satru, uništeni su koj jedan

1030
00:56:15,599 --> 00:56:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] i tada su ponovo, je Izrael došao potpuno u vlast Jeruzalema,

1031
00:56:19,659 --> 00:56:20,679
[SPEAKER_00] svoje glavno grada.

1032
00:56:20,679 --> 00:56:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo proroštvo još nije potpuno ispunjeno.

1033
00:56:25,800 --> 00:56:30,800
[SPEAKER_00] Zato, jer Izraelci da zavape stvarno Mesiji

1034
00:56:30,800 --> 00:56:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] moraju potpuno prestati biti oslonjeni na ljudske snage.

1035
00:56:35,460 --> 00:56:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] Još uvijek je UN i SAD stoja jako uz Izrael.

1036
00:56:40,760 --> 00:56:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] I mora se dogoditi ovo.

1037
00:56:42,059 --> 00:56:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] U onaj dan učinit će Ruzalem teškim kamenom svim narodima.

1038
00:56:45,840 --> 00:56:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] Svi koji ga budu dizali teško će se izranit,

1039
00:56:48,900 --> 00:56:51,059
[SPEAKER_00] a skupit će se na nj svi narodi i zemlje.

1040
00:56:51,059 --> 00:56:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] To je moguće sad.

1041
00:56:52,739 --> 00:56:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tad to nije bilo razumljivo.

1042
00:56:54,380 --> 00:56:56,679
[SPEAKER_00] Danas kad imamo jedinjene narode je to razumljivo.

1043
00:56:56,679 --> 00:57:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] I vjerujte mi, počelo je oštrenje između jedinjenih naroda Izraela.

1044
00:57:01,760 --> 00:57:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] Poznati prorok John Melinde iz Ugande,

1045
00:57:04,480 --> 00:57:06,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji je dao proraštvo i za Hrvatsku,

1046
00:57:06,340 --> 00:57:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] je otišo po Božoj objavi u Izrael par godina prije toga

1047
00:57:11,699 --> 00:57:15,260
[SPEAKER_00] i rekao je mi, uskoro će vas napustiti svi vaši saveznici.

1048
00:57:15,260 --> 00:57:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] I to je propovjedao po sinagogama.

1049
00:57:17,840 --> 00:57:19,719
[SPEAKER_00] I to će se i dogoditi.

1050
00:57:19,719 --> 00:57:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jer tek tad će Izrael stvarno iz srca zavapiti.

1051
00:57:23,539 --> 00:57:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] U njih se sad uvijela oholost zbog podrške koje imaju od SAD-a.

1052
00:57:30,099 --> 00:57:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, evo jedan poznati katolički mistik je također u Jeruzalemu imao otkrivenje.

1053
00:57:35,380 --> 00:57:40,099
[SPEAKER_00] Doći će vrijeme kad će ih napustiti svi njihovi saveznici

1054
00:57:40,099 --> 00:57:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] i kad će se morati osloniti isključivo na jahvu.

1055
00:57:43,920 --> 00:57:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] I tad dolazi 15. proroštvo koje je pred nama

1056
00:57:48,739 --> 00:57:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] nad naravno otkrivenje Mesije Izraelcima.

1057
00:57:51,980 --> 00:57:57,860
[SPEAKER_00] Prorok Zaharija je ovo navijestio 750. prije Krista.

1058
00:57:57,860 --> 00:57:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] I još čekamo da se ispuni.

1059
00:58:01,099 --> 00:58:02,659
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite o ovo proroštvo, molim vas.

1060
00:58:02,659 --> 00:58:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] To je 750. godine prije Krista.

1061
00:58:04,960 --> 00:58:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kad kazna smrti na križu još uopće ne postoji.

1062
00:58:09,079 --> 00:58:10,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Zaharija.

1063
00:58:10,099 --> 00:58:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] Na dom Davidov i na Jeruzalemci izliču duh milosti i molitveni.

1064
00:58:14,960 --> 00:58:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] Gledat će na onoga koga su proboli, naricat će nad njim kao nad jedincem gorkoga oplakivati kao prvenca.

1065
00:58:21,980 --> 00:58:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] Opisuje doslovce pokajanje Izrela koji će gledat onoga koga su proboli i naricat na njim jer će tad postati svjesni da su ubili Mesiju.

1066
00:58:33,159 --> 00:58:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] Zaharija je to najavio i to je pred nama.

1067
00:58:37,000 --> 00:58:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] I znate šta? To se polako događa.

1068
00:58:39,159 --> 00:58:44,900
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bilo uopće židova koji priznao Isusa kao Mesiju kad država Izrael nastale.

1069
00:58:44,900 --> 00:58:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] Danas svi mesijanski židovi su najbrže rastuča sljedba u Izraelu.

1070
00:58:48,840 --> 00:58:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] Najbrže rastuča.

1071
00:58:52,000 --> 00:58:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] Bog polako se objavljuje svom narodu.

1072
00:58:54,380 --> 00:58:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znate ko je fenomen sa židovima?

1073
00:58:56,079 --> 00:58:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] Oni se ne obraćaju evangelizacijom.

1074
00:58:59,480 --> 00:59:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] Moj jedan dobar prijatelj sa velikim karizmanjskim iskustvom je jednom prilikom susrao ateističkog židovskog biznismena

1075
00:59:06,500 --> 00:59:12,739
[SPEAKER_00] i rekuje ja nisam imao nikakve moći pred njim, nikakve snage, nikakvog proročkog pomazanja.

1076
00:59:12,739 --> 00:59:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] Neće Izrael biti obraćen tako što će ga crkva evangelizirati, nego će im se Mesija nad naravno objaviti.

1077
00:59:22,000 --> 00:59:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] I kad god gledate poznata židovska obraćenja, kao što je recimo Ruth Baker, žena Dereka Prinsa,

1078
00:59:27,500 --> 00:59:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] ili još bolje Edith Stein, svetica, redovito su oni imali objavu gdje im se Isus Krist pokazao kao Mesija.

1079
00:59:38,179 --> 00:59:43,699
[SPEAKER_00] U Izraelu je to tema o kojoj se uopće ne smije govoriti.

1080
00:59:43,699 --> 00:59:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] Tu se doslovce šake, u najboljem šake, a u boljem u govorim slučaju noževi i kamenje.

1081
00:59:49,599 --> 00:59:54,780
[SPEAKER_00] Znači i dalje je to kamen s poticanja, međutim sve više i više mesijanskih židova.

1082
00:59:54,780 --> 01:00:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] Htio bih da pogledate ovaj video, kratki, koji će vas uvesti u jednu fascinantnu situaciju koja se dogodila 2008. godine.

1083
01:00:03,340 --> 01:00:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] Može samo svijetla da se malo prijuši.

1084
01:00:10,099 --> 01:00:34,320
[SPEAKER_02] On April 30, 2007, Israel Today ran this amazing headline story, Rabbi Reveals the Name of the Messiah.

1085
01:00:34,320 --> 01:00:40,119
[SPEAKER_03] Speaking to you right here from Tel Aviv, Israel, and today we have a special presentation.

1086
01:00:40,119 --> 01:00:48,159
[SPEAKER_03] We are with one of Rabbi Kaduri's disciples who believes that Yeshua is the Messiah of Israel.

1087
01:00:48,159 --> 01:00:54,739
[SPEAKER_02] Rabbi Yitzhak Kaduri was famously known for his memorization of the Bible, the Talmud, and other Jewish writings.

1088
01:00:55,159 --> 01:01:00,260
[SPEAKER_02] He was a teacher and a revered master at Nahalat Yitzhak Yeshiva seminary.

1089
01:01:00,260 --> 01:01:09,260
[SPEAKER_02] He knew Jewish sages and celebrities of the last century and rabbis who lived in the Holy Land who kept the faith alive before the state of Israel was even born.

1090
01:01:09,260 --> 01:01:15,659
[SPEAKER_02] Kaduri was not only highly esteemed because of his age of 108, but he was charismatic and wise.

1091
01:01:16,159 --> 01:01:18,559
[SPEAKER_02] The chief rabbis looked up to him as a righteous man.

1092
01:01:18,559 --> 01:01:21,820
[SPEAKER_02] Thousands visited him to ask for counsel or healing.

1093
01:01:21,820 --> 01:01:26,539
[SPEAKER_02] His followers speak of many miracles, and his students say that he was a prophet.

1094
01:01:26,539 --> 01:01:34,219
[SPEAKER_03] We are with one of Rabbi Kaduri's disciples who believes that Yeshua is the Messiah of Israel.

1095
01:01:34,219 --> 01:01:43,159
[SPEAKER_03] And before we meet our new friend, Eliyahu, I'd like to take this opportunity to explain to the viewers around the world who Rabbi Kaduri was.

1096
01:01:43,159 --> 01:01:48,320
[SPEAKER_03] Rabbi Kaduri was one of the big known rabbis here in Israel.

1097
01:01:48,320 --> 01:01:50,900
[SPEAKER_03] He had a lot of influence on the government.

1098
01:01:50,900 --> 01:01:52,420
[SPEAKER_03] He had influence on other rabbis.

1099
01:01:52,420 --> 01:01:54,000
[SPEAKER_03] He was one of the top leaders.

1100
01:01:54,000 --> 01:01:59,360
[SPEAKER_03] And he passed away several years ago at the age of 108 years old.

1101
01:02:00,159 --> 01:02:07,840
[SPEAKER_02] A few months before Kaduri died at the age of 108, he surprised his followers when he told them that he had personally met the Messiah.

1102
01:02:07,840 --> 01:02:10,059
[SPEAKER_02] The Messiah had appeared to him.

1103
01:02:10,059 --> 01:02:13,519
[SPEAKER_02] He wrote the name of the Messiah in a note, he said.

1104
01:02:13,519 --> 01:02:17,039
[SPEAKER_02] His official website had mentioned the Messiah note.

1105
01:02:17,039 --> 01:02:26,619
[SPEAKER_02] David Kaduri, the rabbi's 80-year-old son, confirmed that in his last year, his father had talked and dreamed almost exclusively about the Messiah and his coming.

1106
01:02:26,619 --> 01:02:29,780
[SPEAKER_02] My father has met the Messiah in a vision, he said.

1107
01:02:30,159 --> 01:02:32,900
[SPEAKER_02] And he told us that he was coming very soon.

1108
01:02:32,900 --> 01:02:43,639
[SPEAKER_03] Rabbi Kaduri has told his son several times that he had an encounter with the Messiah of Israel, but did not say who that Messiah was.

1109
01:02:43,639 --> 01:02:52,099
[SPEAKER_03] In the Day of Atonement, Yom Kippur, Rabbi Kaduri gave a message in the synagogue saying that the Messiah is coming.

1110
01:02:52,260 --> 01:02:55,719
[SPEAKER_03] And only through his blood will we ever have redemption of sins.

1111
01:02:55,719 --> 01:03:02,519
[SPEAKER_03] He passed away and he left the note not to be opened only one year after his burial.

1112
01:03:02,519 --> 01:03:04,539
[SPEAKER_03] The note was opened.

1113
01:03:04,539 --> 01:03:10,559
[SPEAKER_03] It caused a riot here in Israel when the note said that Yeshua is the Messiah of Israel.

1114
01:03:10,559 --> 01:03:11,420
[SPEAKER_03] Praise God.

1115
01:03:11,599 --> 01:03:18,219
[SPEAKER_02] Kaduri gave a message in his synagogue on Yom Kippur, the Day of Atonement, teaching how to recognize the Messiah.

1116
01:03:18,219 --> 01:03:23,920
[SPEAKER_02] He also mentioned that the Messiah would appear to Israel after Ariel Sharon passed.

1117
01:03:24,599 --> 01:03:37,679
[SPEAKER_02] When Kaduri died, January the 28th, 2006, more than 200,000 people joined the funeral procession on the streets of Jerusalem to pay their respects as he was taken to his final resting place.

1118
01:03:37,679 --> 01:03:47,460
[SPEAKER_02] Shortly before he died, this teacher of Israel wrote the name of the Messiah on a small note which he requested would remain sealed for one year.

1119
01:03:48,139 --> 01:03:52,079
[SPEAKER_02] One year later, the note was opened in 2007.

1120
01:03:52,079 --> 01:03:55,980
[SPEAKER_02] When the note was opened, it read as follows.

1121
01:03:55,980 --> 01:04:05,099
[SPEAKER_02] Concerning the letter abbreviation of the Messiah's name, he will lift the people and prove that his word and law are valid.

1122
01:04:05,099 --> 01:04:11,519
[SPEAKER_02] The Hebrew sentence with the hidden name of the Messiah reads like this.

1123
01:04:13,000 --> 01:04:30,860
[SPEAKER_02] The acronym of that sentence, that is the letter abbreviation that Kaduri spoke of, or the first initials of each word, spell the Hebrew name of Jesus, or Yehoshua, or Yeshua, the Hebrew root word of salvation.

1124
01:04:34,000 --> 01:04:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo se dogodilo od 2008. godine i sad da je to bilo ko drugi rekao, to ne bi toliko potresao Izrael, ali ovo je bio najcijenjeniji rabin u Izraelu.

1125
01:04:44,199 --> 01:04:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek imao 108 godina.

1126
01:04:45,820 --> 01:04:48,599
[SPEAKER_00] Znao je na pamet Talmud i Toru.

1127
01:04:48,599 --> 01:04:56,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jednom prilikom kad je u Jeruzalemu spaljena knjižnica bili su izgubljeni neki tekstovi i spašeni su isključivo zato da ih je on znao na pamet.

1128
01:04:57,139 --> 01:05:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] I bio je karizmatik i prorok vezan sa jako puno ozdravljenja.

1129
01:05:00,659 --> 01:05:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, on je bio mudar i rekao je, tek godinu dana nakon što umrem, ovo otvorite.

1130
01:05:06,079 --> 01:05:08,900
[SPEAKER_00] Zato da umre sa svim počestima i da mu ime ostane.

1131
01:05:08,900 --> 01:05:15,699
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon godinu dana su otvorili i videli da on objavio ime Mesije kao Ješua, odnosno Isus Krist.

1132
01:05:17,980 --> 01:05:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da se Bog uvijek da znak koji će potvrditi proroštvo.

1133
01:05:22,079 --> 01:05:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno, Ariel Sharon kad je umro, kad Uri je bio čovjek dobrog zdravlja.

1134
01:05:26,900 --> 01:05:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] Tad je pao u komu, isto iznenada, i bio je točno 8 godina u komi do objave.

1135
01:05:33,420 --> 01:05:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači vidimo kako je Bog dao potvrdu tom znaku.

1136
01:05:40,179 --> 01:05:47,840
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što se događa i mi živimo u tom vremenu u kojem će Izrael zavapiti Mesiju i prepoznati Isusa.

1137
01:05:47,840 --> 01:05:57,360
[SPEAKER_00] I htio bih malo vas tu dovesti na jedan nov pogled na priču o Josipu Egipatskom.

1138
01:05:57,360 --> 01:05:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je bilo kod Josipa?

1139
01:05:59,420 --> 01:06:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] Josip je živio među svojom braćom.

1140
01:06:02,400 --> 01:06:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog je odlučio po njemu blagosloviti tu braću.

1141
01:06:06,079 --> 01:06:12,179
[SPEAKER_00] I pokaza mu je to u snu, kako mu se klanjaju oni kao klasije, kao zvijezde.

1142
01:06:12,179 --> 01:06:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, oni su ga izavisti prodali u roblje. Odrekli su ga se.

1143
01:06:18,139 --> 01:06:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] Znate koji od braće je predložio da se Josipa proda?

1144
01:06:24,460 --> 01:06:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] Juda i to za 20 srebrnika.

1145
01:06:27,460 --> 01:06:33,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite simboliku. Juda od svih njih kaže ajmo ga prodati za 20 srebrnika.

1146
01:06:33,099 --> 01:06:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] I dolazi kolona Ishmaelaca i on dolazi u Egipat i postaje blagoslov za Egipat.

1147
01:06:39,539 --> 01:06:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] I onda dolazi nevolja gladi na Izrael i ta nevolja njih prisili da dođu natrag k njemu u Egiptu.

1148
01:06:49,079 --> 01:06:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] I tu im se on objavi.

1149
01:06:52,239 --> 01:07:03,420
[SPEAKER_00] Onaj kojeg su se odrekli, kojeg su prodali, kojeg su željeli ubiti, on postaje njihovo rješenje i otkrije se pred njima i tu nastaje njihovo pokajanje.

1150
01:07:03,420 --> 01:07:06,659
[SPEAKER_00] To isto će se dogoditi s izraelskim narodom.

1151
01:07:06,659 --> 01:07:14,179
[SPEAKER_00] On je prodao Isusa za srebrnike, ubili su ga, izgnali su ga i njega i njegove učenike.

1152
01:07:14,179 --> 01:07:20,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ti učenici su postali blagoslov za poganski svijet na isti način na koji je Josip postao blagoslov za Egipat.

1153
01:07:20,639 --> 01:07:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] I kad dođe nevolja, a nevolja je bila glad, a ovdje će ta nevolja biti to da će sav svijet ustati protiv Izrela,

1154
01:07:28,300 --> 01:07:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] oni će zavapiti i potražiti spasenje.

1155
01:07:30,940 --> 01:07:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] I onda, kao što je Josip Egipatski potjerao sve iz te prostorije, sve Egipčane i na samo se otkrije svoje braći,

1156
01:07:41,920 --> 01:07:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] tako će se Isus otkriti Izraelcima ponovo u to vrijeme.

1157
01:07:48,159 --> 01:07:50,780
[SPEAKER_00] Što to nije fascinantno.

1158
01:07:53,780 --> 01:08:01,179
[SPEAKER_00] Jel' svačate koliko je Bog vjeran svoje riječi, koliko je sve simbolički već zapisano i najavljeno?

1159
01:08:01,179 --> 01:08:08,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je samo jedno. Ja sam mogao govoriti temu o najavi Isusa kao Mesije, o planu sa crkvom.

1160
01:08:08,760 --> 01:08:11,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje se samo držim jedne teme, 16 proroštava.

1161
01:08:11,880 --> 01:08:18,899
[SPEAKER_00] Počnite čitat Bibliju kao svjetlo za svoj život.

1162
01:08:18,899 --> 01:08:21,899
[SPEAKER_00] Božja riječ nozija moje svjetiljka.

1163
01:08:23,159 --> 01:08:28,920
[SPEAKER_00] U vremenu progona koja je pred nama opstače samo ljudi koji će razmišljati na taj način.

1164
01:08:28,920 --> 01:08:34,260
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se onog Armenca i onih koji su joj poslušali, sjetite se Jeruzalema.

1165
01:08:34,260 --> 01:08:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se onog čovjeka koji je pobigo iz Vukovara.

1166
01:08:37,920 --> 01:08:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] I sjetite se toga da ulazimo u vrijeme u kojem će se počnati ispunjavati međugorske tajne.

1167
01:08:45,159 --> 01:08:51,840
[SPEAKER_00] Kad povidjeli Cimiranić, čiju sam knjigu pročitao, upravo kaže sad je vrijeme milosti dok treba ukazanja,

1168
01:08:51,939 --> 01:08:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] onda dolazi vrijeme tajni koje neće biti ugodno.

1169
01:08:54,960 --> 01:09:03,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Isus kaže, kad vidite da se to počinje događati, podignite glave jer se približilo vaše spasenje.

1170
01:09:05,199 --> 01:09:09,979
[SPEAKER_00] I videoci se svi slažu da tako mogu gledati jedino oni koji su ukorijenjeni u Bogu.

1171
01:09:09,979 --> 01:09:17,460
[SPEAKER_00] Karl Rahner, teologi, rekao da će kršćani 21. stoljeća ili biti mistici, ili ih neće biti.

1172
01:09:18,039 --> 01:09:20,340
[SPEAKER_00] I Boga mi je dao dovoljno vremena za pripremu.

1173
01:09:20,340 --> 01:09:28,319
[SPEAKER_00] Cijelo 20. stoljeće je bilo vrijeme u kojem je Duh Sveti polako lazi u crkvu kroz karizmatski pokret i podizao je.

1174
01:09:29,060 --> 01:09:37,340
[SPEAKER_00] Proroštva, snovi, vizije, nadnaravna iskustva među lajcima, posvećenje lajka kroz opus DNA katekumene.

1175
01:09:37,340 --> 01:09:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] I sad dolazimo u to vrijeme kad opstaju samo oni koji će imati taj nadnaravni odnos sa živim Bogom.

1176
01:09:46,180 --> 01:09:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pratite znakove vremena i pratite šta se događa s Izraelom, jer sve ovisi o tome.

1177
01:09:52,119 --> 01:09:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerite mi, ovo je prevažno, vidli ste.

1178
01:09:54,920 --> 01:09:59,659
[SPEAKER_00] Nastao sam ukratko pokazati da sve ovisi o tome.

1179
01:09:59,659 --> 01:10:06,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što se još mora dogoditi u Jeruzalemu je obnova hrama i mora se pojaviti Antikrist u hramu.

1180
01:10:06,439 --> 01:10:14,399
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže u Materu Evanđelju da se Antikrist pojavljuje kao grozota pustoši u hramu u Jeruzalemu.

1181
01:10:14,399 --> 01:10:16,600
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi se on pojavio hram, mora biti obnovljen.

1182
01:10:16,600 --> 01:10:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] U Izraelu postoji institut za izgradnju hrama koji je već napravio cijeli nacrt i ima spremanj materijal.

1183
01:10:24,000 --> 01:10:30,560
[SPEAKER_00] Samo što je sad na tom mjestu Omerova džamija i Alaksa, muslimansko svetište.

1184
01:10:30,560 --> 01:10:35,600
[SPEAKER_00] A Izraelci, vjerujte mi, koliko sam ih proučavao i koliko ih poznajem,

1185
01:10:35,600 --> 01:10:41,020
[SPEAKER_00] oni neće ići ni milimetar dalje od onog gdje je gospodin za crta da treba biti hram.

1186
01:10:41,859 --> 01:10:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] I kuha se već. Izrael je izašao iz UNESCO.

1187
01:10:45,500 --> 01:10:50,060
[SPEAKER_00] 2015. godine je premjer Netanyahu je rekao ovako,

1188
01:10:50,060 --> 01:10:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] reći da Izrael nema veze s brdom hrama i zapadnim zidom je kao da kažete da Kina nema veze s kineskim zidom

1189
01:10:56,260 --> 01:10:59,020
[SPEAKER_00] ili da Egipat nema veze s egipatskom piramidom.

1190
01:11:00,020 --> 01:11:05,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ovom odlukom UNESCO je izgubio ono malo legitimiteta što mu je bilo ostalo.

1191
01:11:05,859 --> 01:11:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su izašli. Sve se priprema. Vjerujte mi, nešto će se zakuhat negdje, paš će neka bomba, reći će, eto, bum, sve se srušilo, sad imamo priliku graditi hram.

1192
01:11:16,979 --> 01:11:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] Samo čekaj se. Hram se mora obnoviti. Antikriz će se pojaviti baš u tom hramu.

1193
01:11:23,199 --> 01:11:25,220
[SPEAKER_00] To je sveto pismo.

1194
01:11:26,979 --> 01:11:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon što je Izrael prepozna svog mesiju, dolazi ovo zadnje proroštvo koje ćemo slaviti u nedelju, u 16.

1195
01:11:34,340 --> 01:11:37,760
[SPEAKER_00] To je dolazak mesije u slavi.

1196
01:11:37,760 --> 01:11:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] Najavljeno 750. godine po Zahari i najavljeno i po mnogim drugima.

1197
01:11:45,880 --> 01:11:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] Isus sam je rekao, doći ću, gledat ćete sina čovječe gdje se dolazi na oblacima.

1198
01:11:50,380 --> 01:11:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] Čekamo.

1199
01:11:51,720 --> 01:11:55,239
[SPEAKER_00] I znate šta? Izraelci isto čekaju.

1200
01:11:56,979 --> 01:12:04,100
[SPEAKER_00] Izraelci isto čekaju kada će to biti.

1201
01:12:04,100 --> 01:12:06,140
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mi moramo raditi do tada?

1202
01:12:06,140 --> 01:12:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo bih htio nakon ovog predavanja da promijenite svoj stav o Izraelu.

1203
01:12:10,539 --> 01:12:19,340
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatski narod je bio isto tako inficiran kroz nacizam i fašizam sa mržnjom prema židovima.

1204
01:12:19,340 --> 01:12:21,979
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi, ne isplati se.

1205
01:12:21,979 --> 01:12:25,939
[SPEAKER_00] Čitu sam svjedočanstvo ovdje o čovjeku.

1206
01:12:26,979 --> 01:12:35,279
[SPEAKER_00] Derek Prince je napisao knjigu Blagoslovi prokledstvo i kaže da jedan od najčešćih uzroka prokledstva je i antisemitizam.

1207
01:12:35,279 --> 01:12:41,760
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mislite, kako vam zvuči ovaj riječ koju je Bog rekao Izraelskom narodu, a koji danas stoje?

1208
01:12:41,880 --> 01:12:43,800
[SPEAKER_00] Prokled bio ko tebe proklinje.

1209
01:12:43,800 --> 01:12:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] Blagoslovljen bio ko te blagoslije, prokled bio ko tebe proklinje.

1210
01:12:50,180 --> 01:12:52,359
[SPEAKER_00] Koji te budu kleli i njih ću proklinjati.

1211
01:12:52,359 --> 01:12:56,279
[SPEAKER_00] To su samo neke određe koje je Bog rekao Izraelskom narodu.

1212
01:12:56,279 --> 01:13:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] I sad on donosi svjedočanstvo jednog mladića koji je bio palestinac, izraelski arab i došao je u Ameriku i postoje jako uspješan.

1213
01:13:06,239 --> 01:13:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] Boga čak je kupio franšizu za McDonald's i posto kršćanin.

1214
01:13:10,199 --> 01:13:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] Obratio se ne do njegove propovjedi i dalje ga je mučilo.

1215
01:13:14,039 --> 01:13:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] On na točnom obraćenju teške depresije u koje je padao i redovito bi nakon molitva oslobađanja povraćao bijelu sluz.

1216
01:13:21,000 --> 01:13:29,560
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan od fenomena koji nije toliko rijedak, ali evo, znači te dvije stvari i plus prokledstvo nedostatnosti.

1217
01:13:29,560 --> 01:13:34,899
[SPEAKER_00] Iako je radio sa velikim svotama novca, uvijek je falilo.

1218
01:13:35,039 --> 01:13:38,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mu je trebalo 750 tisuća, on je imao 500 tisuća.

1219
01:13:38,479 --> 01:13:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] I to ga je dovelo i do bankrota.

1220
01:13:40,500 --> 01:13:43,399
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je Isusu postavio ovakvo pitanje.

1221
01:13:43,399 --> 01:13:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite, on sigurno da nije očekivao ovakav odgovor.

1222
01:13:46,920 --> 01:13:56,899
[SPEAKER_00] U tom vapaju jednom, iako je obraćen ništa nije išlo, kaže ovako

1223
01:13:56,899 --> 01:14:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] Jednom sam rekao Bogu, kako si ti velik, stvorio si svemir i sve što je u njemu.

1224
01:14:01,500 --> 01:14:04,020
[SPEAKER_00] On me opitao, vjerujem li zaista u to?

1225
01:14:04,539 --> 01:14:05,899
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, odvratio sam.

1226
01:14:05,899 --> 01:14:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] A onda je rekao, Isus njemu kaže, a što je sa židovskim narodom?

1227
01:14:10,159 --> 01:14:12,239
[SPEAKER_00] U srcu još uvijek ga iši mržnju prema njima.

1228
01:14:12,239 --> 01:14:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetio sam se kako je moja obitelj od uvijek proklinjala židove i učili su me da ih mrzim.

1229
01:14:17,979 --> 01:14:23,060
[SPEAKER_00] S toga sam rekao, odrićem se svake mržnje prema židovskom narodu i opraštam im.

1230
01:14:23,060 --> 01:14:25,560
[SPEAKER_00] U tom se trenutku nešto promijenilo u meni.

1231
01:14:25,560 --> 01:14:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga sam pročitao da je Bog Abrahamu, pravocu židova, rekao,

1232
01:14:30,180 --> 01:14:35,939
[SPEAKER_00] blagoslivljaću oni koji te blagoslivljali budu, koji te budu kleli, njih ću proklinjati.

1233
01:14:35,939 --> 01:14:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tada sam shvatio da se moje financije nalazile pod prokletstvom nedostatnosti.

1234
01:14:41,340 --> 01:14:46,560
[SPEAKER_00] No sloboda je konačno došla. Godine 1982. Bog me oslobodio od prokletstva

1235
01:14:46,560 --> 01:14:51,819
[SPEAKER_00] vezane uz moje financije i antisemitizam. Prihodi su počeli rasti, a sve troškove...

1236
01:14:51,819 --> 01:14:55,600
[SPEAKER_00] Prihodi su ubrzo počeli nadrastati sve troškove koje sam imao.

1237
01:14:55,600 --> 01:15:00,859
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam više problema sa depresijom i slobodno mogu reći kako živim pobjednostnim životom.

1238
01:15:00,859 --> 01:15:06,560
[SPEAKER_00] Svojim sam svjedočanstvom pomogao mnogima da prime oslobođenje i upoznaju Božje blagoslove.

1239
01:15:06,560 --> 01:15:10,560
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo kakvu tešku posljedicu je imao njegov stav.

1240
01:15:11,340 --> 01:15:13,640
[SPEAKER_00] Koji imao prema izraelskom narodu.

1241
01:15:13,640 --> 01:15:20,140
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Bog cijeni ono što je Izrael napravio.

1242
01:15:20,140 --> 01:15:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su udarili temelje.

1243
01:15:21,800 --> 01:15:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, lako je danas biti vjernik.

1244
01:15:24,180 --> 01:15:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] Vi imate neki problem, odete upišete bitno net,

1245
01:15:26,659 --> 01:15:31,020
[SPEAKER_00] pronađete još 50 svjedočanstava s ljudi koji imaju sličan problem,

1246
01:15:31,020 --> 01:15:37,699
[SPEAKER_00] 16 svetaca koji su to prošli i još 14-15 molitvenih zajednica gdje možete potražiti pomoć.

1247
01:15:37,699 --> 01:15:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] Abraham nije imao nikoga.

1248
01:15:41,779 --> 01:15:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kad me Bog rekao, idi iz ove zemlje u zemlju koju ću ti pokazati,

1249
01:15:44,920 --> 01:15:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] nije se mogo sjetiti, aha, Bog je već nekom govorio,

1250
01:15:47,619 --> 01:15:49,560
[SPEAKER_00] je li se posavjetovati sa svojim duhovnikom?

1251
01:15:49,560 --> 01:15:51,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ništa.

1252
01:15:51,600 --> 01:15:54,159
[SPEAKER_00] Izraelski narod je sačuvao vjeru jednog Boga,

1253
01:15:54,159 --> 01:15:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] okružen milijunima, milijunima drugih poganskih naroda do naših dana.

1254
01:15:59,720 --> 01:16:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog kaže, kad kaže Jeruzaleme grade čvrsto sazdani kao jednostali veni,

1255
01:16:05,300 --> 01:16:08,479
[SPEAKER_00] draža su mi vrata Sijonska nego svi šatori Jakovljevi.

1256
01:16:08,479 --> 01:16:14,020
[SPEAKER_00] Bog neće zaboraviti na svoj narodi obećanje koje je dao.

1257
01:16:15,180 --> 01:16:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] I znate, oni koji dolaze tu svaki dan, oni svi mole i ta molitvara kad se prevede direktno sa hebreskog

1258
01:16:24,159 --> 01:16:29,199
[SPEAKER_00] je podsjećanje Boga da se sjeti svojeg obećanja i da obnovi sve to mjesto.

1259
01:16:29,199 --> 01:16:34,279
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog će ih uslišiti, sad nemam tu vide, dok sam gledao te videe nisam mogao vjerovat

1260
01:16:34,279 --> 01:16:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] s kojim žarom mala djeca, tineđeri, invalidi dolaze i plaću.

1261
01:16:39,619 --> 01:16:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] To se ne može glumiti tamo i podsjeće o Boga da ih se sjeti.

1262
01:16:43,920 --> 01:16:47,979
[SPEAKER_00] I znate šta, Bog će ih se sjetiti, jer je on vjeran svoje riječi.

1263
01:16:47,979 --> 01:16:55,060
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što nije uspio egipatski faraon, ono što nije uspjelo Tiglath Pilesaru III.

1264
01:16:55,060 --> 01:16:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] koji ih je odvojio Asirsko sužanstvo, ono što nije uspjelo Nabucadonozor

1265
01:16:59,079 --> 01:17:04,060
[SPEAKER_00] koji ih je potpuno probao zatrt, ono što nije uspjelo Tito Vespanzijan,

1266
01:17:04,060 --> 01:17:07,520
[SPEAKER_00] ono što nisu uspjeli Hitler i Mussolini,

1267
01:17:08,479 --> 01:17:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] ono što nisu uspjeli Arapi, kad su ih 67. napali,

1268
01:17:11,819 --> 01:17:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] neće uspjeti niko.

1269
01:17:13,739 --> 01:17:17,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je Bog vjeran u obećanju kojim je dao.

1270
01:17:17,779 --> 01:17:20,659
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog je vjeran u obećanju koje je dao Abrahamu,

1271
01:17:20,659 --> 01:17:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] a mi trebamo promatrati i čuti Davidov savjet

1272
01:17:24,500 --> 01:17:27,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji je u psalmu rekao, molite za mir Jeruzalemov.

1273
01:17:27,340 --> 01:17:30,399
[SPEAKER_00] To je vaš stav i to je vaš dio.

1274
01:17:30,399 --> 01:17:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

